{"type":"message","id":"9d0c49b4","parentId":"845bd3ad","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:43:31.354Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_EDNOLzwbOJuo9uHjVv7KUFQN|fc_0c3abcc532bcb4ed0169cd5942542c8191b1b5f74e72811703","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b8b184ac-d733-4a46-a6f3-dbe3877d1496\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"daily-openclaw-git-backup\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774361618484,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775014800037,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"30 22 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run the script `C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\scripts\\\\daily-backup-to-branch.cmd` on the host. It should perform a brute-force git backup of `C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw` to branch `backup`. After running it, report success or the exact failure in one short message. Do not modify the script unless execution fails and the fix is obvious.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775100600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775014200017,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 600020,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 2,\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\",\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"03b29602-b584-4ec0-9241-b0d74393cc82\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Atlas OS review - morning\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774388052968,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775050200034,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Revisa el Tasks Tracker de Notion (DB id: 32f0a0b1-97cc-81a8-9443-df3f85f2ffc7, dentro de la página 'Atlas OS - Home' id: 32f0a0b1-97cc-8115-9e62-ec8765ad533c) y úsalo como dashboard operativo. Flujo obligatorio: (1) Lee todas las tareas del tracker; (2) por cada tarea con estado Backlog o Next y dueño claro, coordina activamente al agente responsable (Prometeo, Ares, Hestia o Atlas); (3) exige decisión, primer paso concreto o bloqueo explícito; (4) si un subagente no responde o queda ambiguo, destrábalo o escálalo; (5) actualiza el estado en el tracker según resultado real: usa siempre Backlog, Next, In progress, Waiting, Blocked o Done; (6) nunca marques Done sin confirmación real de entrega; (7) al final envía a WhatsApp +573183718246 un resumen breve: qué moviste, qué coordinaste, qué quedó bloqueado y qué sigue.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 1800\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"to\": \"+573183718246\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775134800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775048400019,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 1800015,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 2,\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\",\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b824f7b0-7497-4984-b0ff-d1bd45539f3c\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"daily-email-review-and-whatsapp-reminder\",\n      \"enabled\