 - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2aecad9b8b6a3c39\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9d2a1815c9432987\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nManage cron jobs for the Gateway scheduler. Related: Cron jobs: Cron jobs Tip: run openclaw cron --help for the full command surface. Note: isolated cron add jobs default to -- announce delivery . Use --no-deliver to keep output internal. --deliver remains as a deprecated alias for -- announce . Note: one-shot (--at) jobs delete after success by default. Use --keep-after-run to keep them. Note ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9d2a1815c9432987\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4c5ff4ab0d87ce41\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCron Jobs - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4c5ff4ab0d87ce41\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/automation/cron-jobs\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"333188d4a34279cb\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTL;DR Cron runs inside the Gateway ( not inside the model). Jobs persist under ~/. openclaw / cron / so restarts don't lose schedules. Two execution styles: Main session: enqueue a system event, then run on the next heartbeat. Isolated: run a dedicated agent turn in cron :<jobId> or a custom session, with delivery ( announce by default or none). Current session: bind to the session where the cron ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"333188d4a34279cb\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"373c9224c5237dfa\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"373c9224c5237dfa\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7e5cdadbd7d44b84\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhat is OpenClaw ? OpenClaw is a self-hosted gateway that connects your favorite chat apps — WhatsApp , Telegram, Discord, iMessage, and more — to AI coding agents like Pi.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7e5cdadbd7d44b84\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"site:docs.openclaw.ai openclaw delivery announce not-delivered cron whatsapp","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":1398,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"02ac6f329eddd89d\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nOpenClaw Without Setup - Plug-and-Play OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"02ac6f329eddd89d\">>>","url":"https://duckduckgo.com/y.js?ad_domain=myclaw.ai&ad_provider=bingv7aa&ad_type=txad&click_metadata=JBfMDCYjRt4CUi1wZLxzsMETCK7M0yEnLwanXtQkQaia8%2D0j7NzKN6Yxm0S7El4xOdJjlBPcjU%2DaUQdp1076PzKiKkOwuo6suv3xpi_NOhCfJ4gI4yVXJDDT3WT0lh8elQPz1FJ5tHVXBl6lYx7lC3nT_YIYtCbvSS5XOJuDYuw.SNe_uSflHUGmcAxynAfkpQ&rut=27fe205ef1b84c022f58ff35b7fb1aaf782136f0d5806f2450bb20224136f4a4&u3=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bing.com%2Faclick%3Fld%3De8DhLQ6ZNOpc25CzWqqSrXsTVUCUyWyxYSv0v5WKzIj633TQ0lOpNYtzciYPT2fYI3M5IFDnNotQ%2DP%2DBWzeHwmTOeKKVWHY_vd37_3F3QkChTt_aCxCH9bm_NrFbracHOJbZckIQ83wLdxlWUtG59iRqZNlO3xuvStoRlxHfBFRIfsbecSHESi5EsO999O%2DFvqLMzX1wVlB5Tf2WbxR5MKHjYz_mk%26u%3DaHR0cHMlM2ElMmYlMmZteWNsYXcuYWklMmYlM2Z1dG1fc291cmNlJTNkYmklMjZtc2Nsa2lkJTNkZmI5MzU5MzFhZWZlMWZjNDY4YzAzMGZjZjRjZmQyZGY%26rlid%3Dfb935931aefe1fc468c030fcf4cfd2df&vqd=4-273761343940838776467472978204895157509&iurl=%7B1%7DIG%3D4BC0A72A7D774F1BBEEB4B81E74ACA51%26CID%3D367A1C66586E653B36660B485962643C%26ID%3DDevEx%2C5038.1","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6acca9792cf9a50a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSkip installs, servers, and configs. Your OpenClaw is live in minutes. The fastest way to use OpenClaw w