{"type":"message","id":"0db5f240","parentId":"0152dd16","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:42:08.243Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_eI6zwOvJGqdjMtl1gmxx9NTU|fc_0c3abcc532bcb4ed0169cdad5057548191aa04192e9b4c4f7a","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"66f48e60-573d-47b9-94f9-40d29cb19542\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+573183718246\",\n      \"name\": \"Atlas OS follow-up pulse\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775065826799,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775076986841,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 10800000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1775065826799\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Haz una pasada de seguimiento muy corta sobre Atlas OS - Home / Tasks Tracker. No releas todo. Solo revisa tareas que ya estén en In progress, Waiting o Blocked y que tengan owner claro (Prometeo, Ares, Hestia o Atlas). Máximo 3 tareas por corrida. Objetivo: detectar si siguen igual, si ya merecen destrabe, o si toca escalar. Reglas: (1) no inventes trabajo nuevo; (2) si el bloqueo es menor, destrábalo con una instrucción concreta al agente responsable; (3) si depende de Gustavo o de entrega externa no confirmada, déjalo explícito; (4) no marques Done sin confirmación real; (5) solo envía mensaje a WhatsApp +573183718246 si hay novedad real, destrabe real o bloqueo que merezca escalado. Si no hay novedad material, responde sin delivery útil.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 360\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"to\": \"+573183718246\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775087426816,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775076626816,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 360025,\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\",\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 2,\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"5ca10713-4dc9-4044-aeda-6dd2bc570cb4\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:tui-43d69cf6-069a-4921-b97c-b5f76e740c45\",\n      \"name\": \"Atlas OS review - end of day\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774451444116,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775065540389,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 19 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Revisa el Tasks Tracker de Notion (DB id: 32f0a0b1-97cc-81a8-9443-df3f85f2ffc7, dentro de la página 'Atlas OS - Home' id: 32f0a0b1-97cc-8115-9e62-ec8765ad533c) con enfoque liviano. Solo procesa: (1) tareas en estado Next; (2) tareas Blocked o Waiting que lleven tiempo o necesiten destrabe; (3) inbox principal si la primera tabla visible trae responsable claro y acción inmediata. Máximo 3 tareas por corrida. Para cada una: coordina al agente responsable con una instrucción concreta, exige primer paso o bloqueo explícito, y no marques Done sin confirmación real de entrega. Si no hay cambios relevantes, no inventes trabajo. Al final envía a WhatsApp +573183718246 un resumen de máximo 5 bullets: qué moviste, qué quedó bloqueado y cuál es el siguiente paso.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"to\": \"+573183718246\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775088000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775002500053,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 1097812,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"8157ed89-ee52-482d-a791-31181c4fff11\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"evening-email-review-and-calendar-check\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774390767598,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775065702067,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 19 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Review the Gmail inbox of atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com with a strict evening pass. Only capture: (1) unresolved items that still matter today, (2) deadlines within the next 3 days, (3) anything that clearly rolls into tomorrow. Keep it lightweight. If a calendar action is obvious, organize it briefly toward toledo970501@gmail.com; do not over-process. Then send Gustavo a concise WhatsApp evening paneo to +573183718246 with max 5 bullets and the single most important thing for tomorrow.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 420\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"to\": \"+573183718246\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775088000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775001600012,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 900041,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\",\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b8b184ac-d733-4a46-a6f3-dbe3877d1496\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"daily-openclaw-git-backup\",\n    